lead_paragraph: Wallabies utility back Christian Lealiifano has been diagnosed with leukaemia and is undergoing treatment, his Super Rugby club said on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Wallabies Back Lealiifano Diagnosed With Leukaemia-Club
